    developmental: "The developmental invitation is to accept that the heart's path and the soul's forward path will not always run parallel in this lifetime — and to find in that divergence not a failure of integration but a distinctive form of richness. Both must be honored in a life that cannot be lived in a single direction.",
    aphorism: "The life that cannot be lived in a single direction must learn the art of the beautiful detour.",
