    evolutionary: "The relational and aesthetic forces of Venus stand at a critical juncture in the soul's incarnational arc — neither clearly at the past nor clearly at the future, but at the turning point between them. This is the configuration of the planet on the bendings: not past-life comfort and not future-life frontier, but the crossroads itself.",
    developmental: "The developmental task is to consciously choose how Venus serves the soul's forward movement — whether love deepens the incarnational direction or becomes a seductive alternative to it. The square does not resolve itself; it demands active discernment about what love is actually for in this particular life.",
