    evolutionary: "The relational soul arrived with the regenerative force of Pluto already fused into it — suggesting a long history of profound loss, transformation, and rebirth in the relational domain. Love is not decorative here; it is the primary medium through which the soul encounters its own depths and those of others.",
    developmental: "The developmental arc asks the individual to move from love as possession or control — Pluto's shadow expression — toward love as conscious co-transformation. The depth does not need to be renounced; it needs to be made safe for others to enter, which requires the individual to have first descended and returned themselves.",
    aphorism: "The volcano that has learned its own power becomes the ground on which new things grow.",
