    evolutionary: "These forces arrived in cross-purpose: the relational soul's longing for beauty and connection, and the regenerative force that will not allow the surface to remain undisturbed. The friction is the pressure toward genuine depth — toward the love that survives its own shadow and emerges the richer for having faced it.",
