    evolutionary: "The soul arrived carrying both the refined relational capacity of Venus and the liberating force of Uranus fused into a single current. Prior-life work with the breaking of social or cultural relational constraints has deposited itself as a constitutional need for love that does not confine — love as experiment rather than institution.",
